f̶̑i̸̓̄m̸͌s̸̍͝ḩ̸̎e̴̍̏ 🦖 2023-10-18 1:45 PM
other screms can use either one-- they just involve the technique of the mouth to produce its main characteristics like tunnel voice-- the zombie scream, is done by making a tunnel with ur mouth, by pogging while curling the tongue pig squeals, methinks is done by placing the tongue near the roof of the mouth, while holding ur mouth wide sideways, so that the scream makes a whistle-y harmonic that sounds like a pig or cricket then the gutterals (toilet bowls) r made by putting the tongue against the roof of the mouth near the teeth while pogging, so that the scream sounds like a wretching noise
